In re ULROP-HUFF CO. Inc. Appeal of WHITEHOUSE, DAVIS & CO., Inc. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. November 2, 1925.) No. 75. Averill & Tompkins, of Rochester, N. Y. (Arthur Mayer, of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. Isaac Adler, of Rochester, N. Y., for appellee.

Before HOUGH, MANTON and HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order (9 F.[2d] 922) affirmed.
